            <div class="mb-2">
                <h6><strong>A note on transferred credit</strong></h6>
                <p>
                    If you have been awarded transferred credit and so have less than 240 credits at Level 2 or above, the thresholds for each degree class are
                    adjusted pro-rata, down to a minimum of 120. The tool will attempt to take this into account if you add a module with the amount of transferred
                    credit you have been given and set the grade to 'transferred'. Note that degrees with transferred credit are notoriously tricky, so always contact the OU to discuss!
                </p>
            </div>

